org.cs2c.nginlib.monitor
接口 NetworkStatus

public interface NetworkStatus

作者：
Mikes

This interface get the network real-time status info already fetched from remote host. The instance implementing the interface is related with network status of a specific time. The operate is off-line, and the instance state-less.

方法摘要
 float getInputKbPerSec()
          Get current network input rate (kbps) which has already fetched from remote host.
 float getOutputPerSec()
          Get current network output rate (kbps) which has already fetched from remote host.
 

方法详细信息

getInputKbPerSec

float getInputKbPerSec()
Get current network input rate (kbps) which has already fetched from remote host.

返回：
The current network input rate (kbps).

getOutputPerSec

float getOutputPerSec()
Get current network output rate (kbps) which has already fetched from remote host.

返回：
The current network output rate (kbps).
